{"tid":2195083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國押後宣布禁止入口新疆棉製品","createTime":"2020-09-09T02:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T06:24:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"414aa71b99487490667af5e636631b9efb190284","tid":2195083,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"美國押後宣布禁止入口新疆棉製品<br />\n2小時前  Share to Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404863&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=58bd0edf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404863&h=d62afdc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=404863</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國政府押後對新疆棉製品實施入口禁令。<br />\n<br />\n美國原本在周二宣布禁止入口所有新疆棉製品，但因為安排問題，要押後到周末以後才正式公布。<br />\n<br />\n美國海關及邊境保衛局助理局長史密斯接受路透社訪問，指禁令涵蓋新疆棉花的整條供應鏈包括棉紗、紡織品和服裝等，另外蕃茄和相關產品，例如蕃茄醬的出口都會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n他表示有合理但非決定性的證據，證明新疆的棉紡織品和蕃茄的供應鏈，與強迫勞動指控有關，美國會繼續調查，填補當中不足的地方。<br />\n<br />\n中國被指在新疆打壓維吾爾族人，建立「再教育營」強迫勞動，北京一直否認指控，美國早前已制裁一些與新疆政策有關的官員，又禁止部分涉嫌使用新疆強迫勞動的成衣公司，購買美國產品。"},{"pid":"698939a6134db1116f0a0b1491828514f389345b","tid":2195083,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e5e887f4a234be412601e9a80ecfb3e86c454b","tid":2195083,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">所謂「白蟻政策」，說穿了就是對「對敵對國家的滲透」，通過「白蟻精神」，默默地蛀蝕香港以及西方社會。這才能夠實現中共所期待的「拿下全世界」。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好恐怖，原來1967年，中共已經想稱霸世界<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192546</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d38b51c558156004072534316408a0e4f5bf69b1","tid":2195083,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:16:33.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo同無印勁多「新疆」棉 <br />\n之前仲試過以「新疆」棉做招徠"},{"pid":"21cbb43c685895ed274192a9dbb787fe36caf3da","tid":2195083,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d38b51c558156004072534316408a0e4f5bf69b1","tid":2195083,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:16:33.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo同無印勁多「新疆」棉 <br />\n之前仲試過以「新疆」棉做招徠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"你咁講有啲印象<br />\n講到好好咁"},{"pid":"2542b734ae3d7e7affbd871447ffc6db65c9937c","tid":2195083,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21cbb43c685895ed274192a9dbb787fe36caf3da","tid":2195083,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d38b51c558156004072534316408a0e4f5bf69b1","tid":2195083,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:16:33.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo同無印勁多「新疆」棉 <br />\n之前仲試過以「新疆」棉做招徠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"你咁講有啲印象<br />\n講到好好咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4141569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4141569&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=6ba08023\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4141569</a><br />\n<br />\n日本品牌「無印良品」和「優衣庫」最近強打以「新疆棉」為素材的服飾產品，讓抗議中國迫害維吾爾族穆斯林的人士挑起眉毛。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">無印良品</span>官網上的廣告詞是「由新疆全手採的有機棉精織，設計簡潔的無印良品男仕牛津襯衫柔軟透氣」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">優衣庫</span>宣傳的男士扣領襯衫，賣點則是「採用以高品質聞名的新疆棉」。<br />\n<br />\n全人手採仲咁平<br />\n仲唔撚係集中營入面嘅人做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 澳洲好波又係佢地講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}